testsuite.name: Game Entity Tests

testcase.name: Parameterized constructor should set date, hometeamID, and awayteamID
toString() should contain all game information
Setters and getters should work correctly
toString() should handle null values gracefully
hashCode() should be equal for equal objects
Constructor with ID should set all fields
equals() should return true for games with same content
equals() should return false for games with different content
equals() should return false when compared to different type
equals() should return true when object is compared to itself
Should add and delete a game
Default constructor should create empty game
equals() should return false when compared to null
